<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.9.4">
<l>koḷḷeṉṟu kiḷarnteḻunta peruñcelva neruppāka</l>
<l>koḷḷeṉṟu tamamūṭu mivaiyeṉṉa vulakiyaṟkai</l>
<l>vaḷḷalē. maṇivaṇṇā vuṉakaḻaṟkē varumparicu</l>
<l>vaḷḷalcey taṭiyēṉai yuṉataruḷāl vāṅkāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Great wealth as a fire that rises shining, saying “take”,</l>
<l>shrouds [all] in darkness, saying “take”. What are these? The nature of the world,</l>
<l>o donor, sapphire-coloured one. By your grace drag me, [your] servant,</l>
<l>doing a benevolent act, on a way that leads to your ankleted [feet].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
